.TH HSH 1 "August 27 2021" "1" "Simple Shell man page"
.SH NAME
.B hsh
- A simple UNIX command interpreter.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ./hsh
.SH DESCRIPTION
This program is a simple shell. It uses basic features and functions.
.SS Overview
The shell reads lines from the prompt, interprets them, and executes. It compiles all .c files in the repo to create an executable file
.SS Path Search
While searching for the commands, it first looks for an executable by the name in the PATH of env followed by builtin commands by that name.

.SH MODES
.B hsh
Interactive mode
.SS
EXAMPLE:
$ ls -l
.B ./hsh
Non-interactive mode
.SS
EXAMPLE:
$ echo "ls -l" | ./hsh

.SH BUILT-IN COMMANDS
.B env
- prints environment
.B exit
- exits the shell
